definitions.definition: A village in Owston and Newbold parish, Harborough district, Leicestershire , England ( OS grid ref SK774079 ) .
A village and civil parish in the Metropolitan Borough of Doncaster , South Yorkshire , England ( OS grid ref SE549011 ) .
A habitational surname from Old English .
